_sText: MG_FRAGXL_KILLBALL BY UNREAL This an arena map in which you need to eliminate the oposite team like in dodgeball. You can play in both sides of the field, and knives won't inflict damage. Evertime someone dies a new ball will spawn. This map might still have some bugs, if you notice one please report ASAP! Thank you. I hope you like this map, GL & HF. Visit www.FRAGXL.com for more information.
